// Cross-TU inline function resolution: `sub` and `double` live in
// input.20-helpers.k65 and are declared `inline`. Their bodies must be
// substituted at the call sites in this file (no JSR; the linker never sees
// these symbols).

func main @a8 {
    lda #10
    sub(a, #5) -> a
    double(a) -> a
}
